About Cedar

Cedar is an innovative, community-governed utility token on the Solana blockchain, created through the merger of two successful tokens previously on the Binance blockchain. This transition offers former holders an exciting opportunity to participate in a project that combines the strengths of its origins while pioneering as one of the first reward-focused utility tokens on Solana. Cedar is entirely led by its community through a decentralized governance process, ensuring that all key decisions are determined by DAO votes. The DAO empowers token holders to actively shape Cedar's direction and future. A dedicated committee is in place solely to implement the decisions made by the DAO, ensuring that the vision of the community is executed with integrity and transparency. Cedar exemplifies the power of a truly decentralized, reward-focused project, bringing real utility and innovation to the Solana network.
